The '''[[Diocese]] of [[Cingoli]]''' was a Roman Catholic diocese in [[Italy]].

It was founded in the fifth century and in 1725 merged with the [[Diocese of Osimo]] to form the [[Diocese of Osimo e Cingoli]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dc252.html|work=[[Catholic-Hierarchy]]|title=Diocese of Cingoli}}</ref>

It was contained within the [[Papal States]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newadvent.org/cathen/11338a.htm|title=Osimo|work=[[Catholic Encyclopedia]]}}</ref>

