The '''Embassy of Cameroon''' in [[Moscow]] is the [[diplomatic mission]] of [[Cameroon]] in the [[Russian Federation]]. It is located at 35 Bolshaya Ordynka ({{lang-ru|Большая Ордынка, 35}}) <ref>{{cite web |title=Консульские отношения |publisher=[[Ministry of Foreign Affairs (Russia)]] |url=http://www.ln.mid.ru/ns-rafr.nsf/89414576079db559432569d8002421fc/29ff7649782dc03343256c3d0037dbe7?OpenDocument |accessdate=2008-06-25 |language=ar |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110614161351/http://www.ln.mid.ru/ns-rafr.nsf/89414576079db559432569d8002421fc/29ff7649782dc03343256c3d0037dbe7?OpenDocument |archivedate=2011-06-14 |df= }}</ref>
