'''''With Mum''''' ({{lang-bs|'''Sa mamom'''}}) is a 2013 Bosnian [[drama film]] directed by [[Faruk Lončarević]].<ref name="sarajevotimes">{{cite web |url=http://www.sarajevotimes.com/bosnian-film-mum-faruk-loncarevic-compete-oscar-prize/ |title=Bosnian film "With Mum" by Faruk Lončarević to Compete for the Oscar prize |accessdate=14 December 2014 |work=Sarajevo Times}}</ref> It was selected as the Bosnian entry for the [[Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]] at the [[87th Academy Awards]], but was not nominated.<ref name="Bosnia">{{cite web |url=http://www.klix.ba/magazin/film-tv/film-sa-mamom-bh-kandidat-za-nominaciju-za-oscara/140922023|title= Film "Sa mamom" bh. kandidat za nominaciju za Oscara|accessdate=22 September 2014 |work=Klix}}</ref><ref name="HWR">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-bosnia-selects-mom-macedonia-734984 |title=Oscars: Bosnia Selects 'With Mom,' Macedonia 'To the Hilt' for Foreign-Language Category |accessdate=23 September 2014 |work=Hollywood Reporter}}</ref>
==Cast== * [[Marija Pikic]] as Berina * [[Mira Furlan]] as Jasna * [[Branko Djuric]] as Mladen * [[Sanja Vejnovic]] as Kaca * [[Igor Skvarica]] as Tarik * [[Edina Kordic]] as Luna
